Package com.cs546.backend.core.city

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    CityHistory
    This provides functionality to keep track of how the city changes over time.
    CityState
    This contains the nodes and connections that make up the city, and various methods to interact with and manipulate the city.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    City
    City object that wraps up the CityState and contains some statistics about the city.
    CityBuildTool
    Provides functionality to build different components and connections on a city.
    CityData
    This class makes use of the builder pattern alongside the CityDataBuilder class.
    CityDataBuilder
    The other side of the city data builder patter.
    CityHistoryVisualisation
    This provides functionality to generate graph visualisations of the CityHistory.
    CityVisualisation
    This provides functionality that is necessary to visualise the city on the frontend.
    DefaultCityHistory
    A default implementation of CityHistory.
    GameState
    This class is responsible for running the simulation of the city.
    GraphCityState  
    Node
    This class represents each point in the city and has access to its own coordinates as well as the component of which it is
  • Enum Summary

    In short, these are external influences.
